                     <interp inst="t18091101-34-off209" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18091101-34-cd210" type="crimeDate">29th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091101-34-off209 t18091101-34-cd210"></join>, 56 yards of printed callico, value 5 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18091101-34-victim345" type="victimName">
